headline: Starbucks Elects Two Board Members Including Former Yahoo CEO Marissa Mayer

headline: Verizon announces Semtech as ‘Verizon Frontline Verified’ partner
summary: Verizon (VZ) Frontline announced that several products from Semtech (SMTC), formerly Sierra Wireless, have achieved “Verizon Frontline Verified” status. This includes the AirLink XR60 5G Router, which supports the recently-launched Verizon Frontline Network Slice.
